OL,7,FA woman caught throwing litter from
OL,8,Fher vehicle in Buckinghamshire on
OL,9,Fanother driver's dashcam, has become
OL,10,Fthe first person to be issued with a
OL,11,Ffixed penalty notice at the new,
OL,12,Fhigher rate of #500.
OL,14,FOn Monday 9 September 2024, on
OL,15,FFriarage Road in Aylesbury, a vehicle
OL,16,Fwas recorded littering by a dashcam
OL,17,Fbelonging to another driver.
