OL,7,FBuckinghamshire Council's Litter
OL,8,FEnforcement Team launched an
OL,9,Finvestigation and contacted the
OL,10,Fregistered vehicle keeper.
OL,12,FAfter further investigation, a woman
OL,13,Fadmitted to littering while driving
OL,14,Fher vehicle. She was offered a #500
OL,15,FFixed Penalty Notice to discharge her
OL,16,Fliability for prosecution regarding
OL,17,Fthe littering offence.
