OL,7,FThe council say the dashcam footage
OL,8,Fwas crucial for the investigation, as
OL,9,Fit clearly captured the offence,
OL,10,Fincluding the vehicle's registration
OL,11,Fnumber and an image of the litter
OL,12,Fbeing thrown from the driver's side
OL,13,Fwindow.
OL,15,FThomas Broom, Buckinghamshire
OL,16,FCouncil's Cabinet Member for Climate
OL,17,FChange and Environment said: "We take
OL,18,Fa zero-tolerance approach to litter
OL,19,Fand have more than tripled our fixed
OL,20,Fpenalty notices to #500 for the
OL,21,Foffence.
