OL,7,F"This aligns with our "For Bucks
OL,8,FSake!" campaign, aimed at tackling
OL,9,Flittering issues and making everyone
OL,10,Faware that littering of any kind is
OL,11,Fnot acceptable and if we catch you, we
OL,12,Fwill do everything in our power to
OL,13,Fprosecute.
OL,15,F"Littering from a moving vehicle
OL,16,Fdoesn't just spoil the beauty of our
OL,17,Fcommunity, it's a criminal offence and
OL,18,Fit will cost you. Let's keep our roads
OL,19,Fclean and safe, respect the
OL,20,Fenvironment and avoid the penalty."
